data.description: You Will Be Amazed with this HOUSE. Fully Remodeled Home Offering 3,477 Sqft Under Roof, an Open and Inviting Oversized Great Room with Vaulted Ceilings, Open Dining Area and Tastefully Updated Kitchen with HUGE Island. Kitchen with Multi-Colored Cabinets, Quartz Countertops with Waterfall Island, with Seating of 5 Additional Cabinets, Soft Close Cabinets and Drawers, Under Counter Microwave, Stainless Steel Appliances w/ 5 Door Refrigerator and Hood Vent, Pendant Lighting & Tile Backsplash. Master Suite with Tray Ceilings, Sitting area, 2 Walk in Closets, Double Vanities, Soaking Tub with Hand Held Faucet, Mable Cased Shower with 2 Shower Heads and Multi Adjustable Body Spray Heads. Additional 2 Bathrooms are Remodeled with New Vanities and Tile Surrounds. 3 Guest Bedrooms all Oversized with Larger Closets. Bonus Office/ Study or 5th Bedroom. New Roof Before Closing! NO REAR NEIGHBORS- Home Back to a Canal Leading to and Mini Lake. You Do Not Want to Miss this Turnkey Home... Call For a Showing today!
